      "para_id": "Q000908.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninĝirsu , the powerful warrior of Enlil , Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , brought about perfection : he built and restored his E-ninnu-anzud-babbar ."
